title: Ponkor 45W magsafe 2 Power Supply Charger with 2-Port USB for Apple Mac book Air 11 inch and 13 inch
feature: Macbook Air charger compatible with 11'' and 13'' Apple Macbook Air new models that appeared after June. 2012, such as Apple A1436,A1466,A1465,A1435,MD223/4,MD231/2,MD760/1,MD711/2
45W magsafe 2 T-tip connector manufactured with the highest quality technology and fireproof materials against incorrect voltage, short circuit, internal overheating. NEVER SPARK!
2 port USB can charge your iPhone, iPad, Samsung, Android Smartphones and other devices while charging your MacBook air. You can also share power with your family or friends.
Come with a little base to keep everything organized. Can be used with or without the base, both convenient for travelling and business.
Input: 100-240V, 1.5A 50-60Hz. Output: 14.85V 3.05A. 12 months warranty, 30 days money return gurantee, 24*7 email support.
description: - For Apple MacBook Air series:Mid 2012 to Early 2015 11" MacBook Air (11”,early-2015),MJVM2LL/A，MJVP2LL/A MacBook Air (11”,early-2014),MD711LL/B，MD712LL/B MacBook Air (11”,mid-2013),MD711LL/A，MD712LL/A MacBook Air (11”,mid-2012),MD223LL/A，MD224LL/A - For Apple MacBook Air series:Mid-2012 to Early-2015 13" MacBook Air (13”,early-2015),MJVE2LL/A，MJVG2LL/A MacBook Air (13”,early-2014),MD760LL/B，MD761LL/B MacBook Air (13”,mid-2013),MD760LL/A，MD761LL/A MacBook Air (13”,mid-2012),MD231LL/A，MD232LL/A Magsafe 1,5 pins :The middle pin is smaller than other four.
